title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - What's new in the marketplace - week 32
description:
In this video, we're delving into the latest additions to the MSFS 2020 marketplace. This week, the marketplace welcomed several new aircraft and helicopters, featuring the Boeing 777 by PMDG and a Sikorsky helicopter. Additionally, while there are a few new livery packs, there's been a notable increase in the number of new airports available in the store.
